Once a upon a time, there was a very short-tempered demon.He would get angry 
at the smallest things.When angry , he had no control over his actions

One day , the demon decided to make a beautiful tree house for himself.
He worked hard for a week . After some days , a beautiful tree house was ready.
Just when it was ready a pegion flying above dropped a worm on his sholder.

The demon became very furious and started chasing it , after a long time of
chasing the pegion sat on the tree house he made .The demon was so blinded by rage 
he cuts the tree on which the pigeon was sitting crashing down the tree house.

moral of the story - thoughtless anger can cause serious damage